texts.text:
Debug Stick, item used to change various block states.
Debug mode, world type used to test block states.
Debug screen, screen shown when F3 is pressed.
Commands/debug, command used to start and stop debug sessions.
debug.png and debug2.png, debugging assets found in the game's texture files.
Various game versions created for debugging purposes:

Alpha v1.2.2a
Beta 1.3a
Beta 1.6 Test Build 3
Numerous snapshots and pre-releases
